further explanation on Bullish Pennants:Pennants are continuation patterns where aperiod of consolidationis followed by a breakout used in technical analysis.It'simportant to look at the volumein a pennant—the period of consolidation should have lower volume and the breakouts should occur on higher volume.likejOjOpreviously mentioned  Manulife (BTOU) daily chart currently fulfilled all the above conditions - little pullback (consolidation) on lower volumewaiting for the last condition - breakout on high volume😀buy b4 breakout or buy after breakout both involve risk of course
